dct_title_s: Map of Blanchard River Basin (lower portion) showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Blanchard River Basin (Lower portion)
dct_description_sm: Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Blanchard Basin and quality of underground water.
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water, from data compiled by Lawrence R. Brunstetter".
